<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>CivicPulse | Empowering Communities</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary: #6366f1;
      --primary-light: #818cf8;
      --accent: #a855f7;
      --bg: #0f172a;
      --card-bg: rgba(30, 41, 59, 0.7);
      --text-main: #f8fafc;
      --text-muted: #94a3b8;
      --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background-color: var(--bg);
      color: var(--text-main);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      overflow-x: hidden;
      background-image:
        radial-gradient(circle at 20% 20%, rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.15) 0%, transparent 25%),
        radial-gradient(circle at 80% 80%, rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.15) 0%, transparent 25%);
    }

    .hero-container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      width: 100%;
      padding: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
    }

    @keyframes fadeIn {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
      }

      to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }

    .brand-logo {
      font-size: 3.5rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-light), var(--accent));
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      letter-spacing: -2px;
    }

    .hero-subtitle {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto 3rem auto;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .portal-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
      gap: 2rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    .portal-card {
      background: var(--card-bg);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 24px;
      padding: 2.5rem;
      text-decoration: none;
      color: var(--text-main);
      transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .portal-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
      opacity: 0;
      transition: opacity 0.3s;
    }

    .portal-card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-10px);
      border-color: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.5);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
    }

    .portal-card:hover::before {
      opacity: 1;
    }

    .icon-box {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      background: rgba(99, 102, 241, 0.1);
      border-radius: 16px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      color: var(--primary-light);
      transition: transform 0.3s;
    }

    .portal-card:hover .icon-box {
      transform: scale(1.1) rotate(5deg);
    }

    .portal-title {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .portal-desc {
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .footer-note {
      margin-top: 4rem;
      color: var(--text-muted);
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      opacity: 0.6;
    }

    /* SVG Icons */
    .icon {
      width: 32px;
      height: 32px;
      fill: currentColor;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="hero-container">
    <div class="brand-logo">CivicPulse</div>
    <p class="hero-subtitle">
      A smart, AI-powered platform for reporting and tracking civic issues.
      Together, let's build better, safer, and cleaner communities.
    </p>

    <div class="portal-grid">
      <a href="/user-login" class="portal-card">
        <div class="icon-box">
          <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path
              d="M12 12c2.21 0 4-1.79 4-4s-1.79-4-4-4-4 1.79-4 4 1.79 4 4 4zm0 2c-2.67 0-8 1.34-8 4v2h16v-2c0-2.66-5.33-4-8-4z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="portal-title">Citizen Portal</h2>
        <p class="portal-desc">Report potholes, broken lights, or trash. Track your submissions in real-time with
          AI-assisted detailing.</p>
      </a>

      <a href="/admin-login" class="portal-card">
        <div class="icon-box">
          <svg class="icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path
              d="M12 1L3 5v6c0 5.55 3.84 10.74 9 12 5.16-1.26 9-6.45 9-12V5l-9-4zm-2 16l-4-4 1.41-1.41L10 14.17l6.59-6.59L18 9l-8 8z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h2 class="portal-title">Admin Console</h2>
        <p class="portal-desc">Manage city-wide reports, update processing statuses, and analyze community health
          statistics.</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer-note">
      &copy; 2026 CivicPulse Technologies. Powered by Advanced Intelligence.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>